### Agri360 - Mahsoly Crop Prices Integration
### Testing crop prices in Dashboard and Marketplace

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = your_jwt_token_here

### 1. Get Dashboard with Mahsoly Crop Prices (English)
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept-Language: en

### 2. Get Dashboard with Crop Prices (Arabic - Egyptian)
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/stats?lang=ar
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept-Language: ar-EG

### 3. Get Dashboard with Crop Prices (Arabic - Saudi)
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/stats?lang=ar-SA
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. List Marketplace Listings with Market Prices (English)
GET {{baseUrl}}/marketplace/listings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept-Language: en

### 5. List Marketplace Listings with Mahsoly Price Comparison (Arabic)
GET {{baseUrl}}/marketplace/listings?lang=ar
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept-Language: ar-EG

### 6. Create a Market Listing with Price Suggestion from Mahsoly
POST {{baseUrl}}/marketplace/listings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Premium Wheat",
  "description": "High quality wheat from Delta region",
  "crop": "Wheat",
  "quantity": 500,
  "unit": "kg",
  "pricePerUnit": 450,
  "location": "Dakahlia, Egypt"
}

