### 9. Get Marketplace Listings with Full Mahsoly Price Comparison
GET {{baseUrl}}/marketplace/listings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Response includes:
### - listing details (title, description, crop, quantity, unit, price)
### - farmer info (name, email)
### - marketPriceData: Current prices from Mahsoly API
### - priceComparison:
###   * listingPrice: Farmer's listed price
###   * marketPrice: Current market price from Mahsoly
###   * marketCurrency: Currency (EGP)
###   * source: Data source (mahsoly)
